    "description_long": "This is a rectangular, walled graveyard featuring rows of evenly spaced headstones set in a grassy area. The perimeter is defined by a low, white stone wall with two small entrance structures at either end and a central, larger memorial or monument structure. The headstones are arranged in parallel lines, suggesting a formal, organized cemetery layout. The central monument appears to be a focal point, possibly serving as a war memorial or commemorative structure, and is flanked by the headstones. The grass is well-maintained, and the overall appearance is orderly and respectful. The white stone and green grass create a stark, solemn contrast typical of formal cemeteries.",
